        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ccd318/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-13T17:23:52.227Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Can you try whether the home button works by having a friend call you?</p>\n<p>Does the screen-filling notification always happen for you? Because it only happens on the lock screen for me, otherwise it’s just a normal push notification.</p>\n<p>Worth mentioning too: As far as I can see, the caller can’t see whether the call was declined or ignored, only the recipient can. So you might as well just hang up.  :)</p>",
